text: Eden Zanker (born 11 November 1999) is an Australian rules footballer playing for the Melbourne Football Club in the AFL Women's competition (AFLW). Zanker was drafted by Melbourne with the club's first selection and sixth pick overall in the 2017 AFL Women's draft.
